        <text><![CDATA[ <p> <p><b><b>No Money Bail Act of 2019</b></b> <p>This bill restricts the use of money bail (i.e., the payment of money as a condition of pretrial release) in criminal cases. <p>Specifically, it prohibits the use of money bail in federal criminal cases. <p>Additionally, it makes a state that uses a money bail system ineligible for funds under the Edward Byrne Memorial Justice Assistance Grant Program.]]></text>
      </summary>
